<h5 id="subject_1031813">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=114475.msg1031813#msg1031813" rel="nofollow">【APG】秘术(神术专精：审判者圣途、救赎者圣途)(法术专精：绘符学派)</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1031813'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_1031813'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
